data.title: Diamond Seagulls
data.meta_description:
Oh Wow! by Diamond Seagulls, released 13 August 2023

1. Coming Over Your Eyes
2. Love Ain't For Free
3. Paradise Calls
4. Look What The Cat Dragged In
5. The Way She Rides
6. Young and Wild and Free
7. Simple Life
8. Pants on Fire
9. Love Me
10. She's Hot
11. Higher
12. Let's Not Get Drowned
13. Tabledance Bar
14. Seagulls for Tonight

The most essential Glam Rock album of all times. This iconic album takes you out for a ride through Los Angeles and California in the Mid 80s. Punk meets rock with some of the greatest lyrics ever.
